  <desc>One of the biggest rides of the year on the best gravel in the South of England with a weekend packed full of brilliant cycling. Ride the Double Centurion (217km) on the tank tracks, fire roads & gravel trails of Salisbury Plain and the stunning Wiltshire countryside.</desc>
  <link href="https://ridewithgps.com/routes/51612285"/>
  <time>2026-07-18</time>
